Package hospital.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyLogException
    This exception is used to signal that an invalid request has been made to a log object.
    EmptyWaitingRoomException
    This exception arises when a waiting room cannot support a requested action because there are no patients currently waiting.
    InvalidConditionException
    This exception signals that an unsupported emergency condition has been provided to the hospital management system.
    InvalidPriorityException
    This exception is used to signal that an invalid triage priority has been provided to a method in the hospital management system.
